testlink-node-api node module brings a pure JavaScript framework to integrate TestLink tool(test management tool)
By default TestLink providing XML-RPC.api which can be used to get the response from TestLink server.
By using testlink-node-api we can integrate with any javaScript automation tools like Selenium-webdriver.js or webdriver.js for 
executing automation testCases and update the Results in TestLink. It can also be integrated with BDD frameworks 
like Cucumber.js and Yadda.js.

Installation
Node based environments. 

npm install testlink-node-api
